[[File:A632 Matlock to Chesterfield road.jpg|thumb|View looking downhill towards Slatepit Dale and with Chesterfield visible in the distance.]]
The '''A632''' is a major road in [[Derbyshire]] and [[Nottinghamshire]], [[England]]. It starts in Matlock {{nowrap|({{coord|53.1347|-1.5485|type:landmark_region:GB|display=inline|name=A632 road (western end)}})}} and joins the town with [[Chesterfield]]. From there, it goes through [[Bolsover]] and then onto the A616 at the village of [[Cuckney]] {{nowrap|({{coord|53.2336|-1.1543|type:landmark_region:GB|display=inline|name=A632 road (eastern end)}}).}}

