{{Infobox software
| name = Montage
| screenshot = DSS pleiades mosaic.jpg
| caption = Mosaic image of the Pleiades star cluster created with Montage. The blue, green, and red channels of this three- color image were made from B-, R-, and I-band images, respectively, from the [[Digitized Sky Survey|Digitized Sky Survey (DSS)]]. Image credit: Inseok Song (University of Georgia)
| developer = IPAC, JPL, CACR, ISI
| released = {{Start date and age|2003|10|10}}
